ged in another way"}},{"annotations":[],"tagUuids":[],"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","text":"Very many kinds of data are connected to people. If there could be a way for someone, including yourself, to find out who that person is, that is considered personal data.\n\nSimple examples are name, birth day or address; but there are many other data that can be personal: for example a combination of a location and a time, genetic information, or an X-ray of the skull.","uuid":"4e64fff0-1177-4d76-8421-963720fae346","entityUuid":"49c009cb-a38c-4836-9780-8a8b3dd1cbac","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","parentUuid":"b1df3c74-0b1f-4574-81c4-4cc2d780c1af","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"Will you collect any data connected to a person, \"personal data\"?","requiredPhaseUuid":null},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"2eda9560-888d-430e-a492-8730ec2bd920","entityUuid":"4bdc319d-282a-4a80-9cdd-78d2081e812b","parentUuid":"49c009cb-a38c-4836-9780-8a8b3dd1cbac","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"No"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"3153bef8-52a4-4b23-bf16-0e5750dc9dc1","entityUuid":"421e2d3e-c95c-4244-9465-de8f1cb8aeba","parentUuid":"49c009cb-a38c-4836-9780-8a8b3dd1cbac","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"Yes"},{"annotations":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","text":{"changed":false},"uuid":"151cf109-fb1c-405b-b2c2-44f7e59a40a5","questionUuids":{"changed":true,"value":["b08fe063-33f8-4380-b3a9-ba1e586dedf2","2bac9020-99cf-4463-8d34-0b0eb2781cd1","5ba53879-eb48-47f2-a73b-f7f7d83bf030","8c962e6f-17ee-4b22-8ebb-9f06f779e3b3","f87c331d-794a-42c8-a910-61a2a9110dab","f038bd46-ee4e-4f53-b7ea-482381c2c855","ab4b3f39-dfab-45a5-9489-2d46ceacbb73","0e810343-6026-4992-8ea0-5539cbc77093","49c009cb-a38c-4836-9780-8a8b3dd1cbac","f5e162ee-1077-4ebe-a932-192bc7f67e98","cb7d17a8-30c0-489d-a43c-702b27d97611","59cd7bb6-8b24-4a4b-9baa-e7147807c58d"]},"entityUuid":"b1df3c74-0b1f-4574-81c4-4cc2d780c1af","parentUuid":"6f6241d9-136c-4770-9d58-8a3f39607052","eventType":"EditChapterEvent","title":{"changed":false}},{"annotations":[],"tagUuids":[],"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","text":"Many countries, including the European Union, have strict laws that require anyone who processes personal data to do so only with a good reason. The allowed \"good reasons\" are called \"legal base\" for the processing of the data.","uuid":"52d0f3ff-63b8-4077-8e44-bd20c72e5c31","entityUuid":"be4651c9-9a8c-4e10-a158-61b94ca0e139","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","parentUuid":"421e2d3e-c95c-4244-9465-de8f1cb8aeba","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","title":"What legal basis are you using to collect and process the personal data?","requiredPhaseUuid":null},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"4af8fab5-5602-4b3d-9855-56d235557511","entityUuid":"73cd2dda-41ba-456b-9a4e-aa34c78f2fcf","parentUuid":"be4651c9-9a8c-4e10-a158-61b94ca0e139","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"We ask the data subjects for their consent"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"6ef53ca2-5a54-4a51-8382-913704489a7b","entityUuid":"1dfe0a6d-4281-4d5e-bcaa-5e20fa28a591","parentUuid":"be4651c9-9a8c-4e10-a158-61b94ca0e139","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"We require the processing to fulfil our contract with the data subjects"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"ede368d4-1dbe-49fa-a2cd-957daf8773ba","entityUuid":"9d5e3104-2b6b-4d95-848e-253ef069d8b3","parentUuid":"be4651c9-9a8c-4e10-a158-61b94ca0e139","eventType":"AddAnswerEvent","metricMeasures":[],"label":"We have a legitimate interest: data subjects all expect us to do this data processing because of who we are"},{"annotations":[],"advice":null,"createdAt":"2021-11-02T10:22:46.775632Z","uuid":"47712b38-767f-